nodes.text: A group of Humans at one point abducted Duros newlyweds Etro Edthatt and Droza Edthatt. The Humans attacked the aliens with metal sticks and took them to their homeworld of Urthha for a party. After Etro developed collard lesions from eating a potato, the Humans were scared away by the symptoms.

These Human abductors were mentioned in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
